<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SVS — Smart Verification System</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          fontFamily: {
            sans: ['Outfit', 'ui-sans-serif', 'system-ui'],
            mono: ['JetBrains Mono', 'ui-monospace', 'SFMono-Regular'],
          },
          boxShadow: {
            glass: '0 24px 60px rgba(15,23,42,0.12), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.72)',
            card: '0 12px 34px rgba(15,23,42,0.07), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.72)',
          },
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-10 font-sans text-slate-900 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#f7fbff] via-[#ecf4ff] to-[#f8fbff]">
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" style="background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(148,163,184,0.08) 1px, transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(148,163,184,0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:32px 32px;mask-image:radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(0,0,0,.95), rgba(0,0,0,.42));"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" style="background:
        radial-gradient(720px 420px at 12% 10%, rgba(250,204,21,.22), transparent 62%),
        radial-gradient(860px 520px at 100% 0, rgba(29,78,216,.18), transparent 64%),
        radial-gradient(380px 220px at 82% 76%, rgba(220,38,38,.08), transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(420px 280px at 18% 88%, rgba(29,78,216,.08), transparent 72%);"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-5xl text-center px-6 md:px-10 py-12 md:py-14 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-2xl shadow-glass">
    <div class="absolute -left-10 -bottom-10 w-72 h-72 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(250,204,21,0.18),transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute -right-12 -top-12 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(29,78,216,0.16),transparent_72%)] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 mb-8 sm:mb-10">
      <div class="relative w-32 h-32 sm:w-36 sm:h-36 rounded-3xl p-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/15 via-blue-500/10 to-amber-400/25 grid place-items-center shadow-[0_30px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.12),inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.45)]">
        <div class="absolute inset-2.5 rounded-2xl border border-white/80 blur-[0.8px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        <img class="w-full h-full object-contain rounded-2xl drop-shadow-[0_22px_32px_rgba(15,23,42,0.16)]" src="/images/logo.png" alt="MDRRMO SVS Logo">
      </div>
      <div class="text-left sm:text-left">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black tracking-tight">SVS</div>
        <div class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-slate-600 px-3 py-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 shadow-sm">
          <span class="inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 shadow-[0_0_0_6px_rgba(250,204,21,0.16)]"></span>
          Smart Verification System
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-slate-500">
          <span class="inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 shadow-[0_0_0_6px_rgba(250,204,21,0.28)]"></span>
          Instant verification · Live dispatch sync
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <span class="text-[0.66rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 px-3 py-2 rounded-full bg-slate-50/90 border border-slate-200">Quick jump</span>
      <a href="#report" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-amber-200/70 bg-white/90 text-amber-700 font-semibold text-sm shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2 3 14h7l-1 8 10-12h-7Z"/></svg>
        Report in 30s
      </a>
      <a href="#dispatcher" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-blue-200/70 bg-white/90 text-blue-700 font-semibold text-sm shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 6h12M6 12h10M6 18h8"/></svg>
        Monitor live dispatch
      </a>
      <a href="#admin" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 text-slate-700 font-semibold text-sm shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md transition">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 1 7 7v7a7 7 0 0 1-14 0V9a7 7 0 0 1 7-7Z"/></svg>
        Access admin console
      </a>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight mb-3">Select your <span class="text-amber-500">role</span></h1>
    <p class="text-slate-700 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">Choose the interface that matches your role. Reports submitted by citizens appear on the dispatcher console in real time.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
      <a id="report" href="/report" class="group relative flex flex-col text-left p-6 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200/70 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/95 via-white to-amber-50/60 shadow-card overflow-hidden focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-4 focus-visible:outline-amber-300">
        <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-16 w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(250,204,21,0.34),transparent_68%)] opacity-60 group-hover:scale-110 transition"></div>
        <div class="relative w-16 h-16 mb-4 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 grid place-items-center shadow-inner">
          <div class="absolute inset-2 rounded-xl border border-white/70 pointer-events-none"></div>
          <svg class="relative w-6 h-6 text-amber-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[0.65rem] font-bold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-amber-600 mb-1">Citizen</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">Report an Emergency</div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1">Submit an incident report or send an instant Panic SOS to SVS dispatchers.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-amber-700 px-3 py-2 rounded-full border border-amber-200 bg-white/80">
          Open Report Form
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a id="dispatcher" href="/dispatcher/login?force=1" class="group relative flex flex-col text-left p-6 rounded-2xl border border-blue-200/70 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/95 via-white to-blue-50/60 shadow-card overflow-hidden focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-4 focus-visible:outline-blue-300">
        <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-16 w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(29,78,216,0.28),transparent_68%)] opacity-60 group-hover:scale-110 transition"></div>
        <div class="relative w-16 h-16 mb-4 rounded-2xl border border-blue-200 bg-blue-50 grid place-items-center shadow-inner">
          <div class="absolute inset-2 rounded-xl border border-white/70 pointer-events-none"></div>
          <svg class="relative w-6 h-6 text-blue-700" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3.75 6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 3.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 10.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6ZM3.75 15.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 13.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.75 18v-2.25ZM13.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 20.25 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 10.5h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6ZM13.5 15.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 20.25h-2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 13.5 18v-2.25Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[0.65rem] font-bold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-blue-700 mb-1">Dispatcher</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">Operations Dashboard</div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1">Monitor live reports, verify incidents, dispatch response teams, and track resolutions.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700 px-3 py-2 rounded-full border border-blue-200 bg-white/80">
          Dispatcher Login
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a id="admin" href="/login?force=1" class="group relative flex flex-col text-left p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/95 via-white to-slate-50/80 shadow-card overflow-hidden focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-4 focus-visible:outline-slate-300">
        <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-16 w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(37,99,235,0.26),transparent_68%)] opacity-60 group-hover:scale-110 transition"></div>
        <div class="relative w-16 h-16 mb-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 grid place-items-center shadow-inner">
          <div class="absolute inset-2 rounded-xl border border-white/70 pointer-events-none"></div>
          <svg class="relative w-6 h-6 text-slate-800" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m6-3.75a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[0.65rem] font-bold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-slate-700 mb-1">Admin</div>
        <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">Admin Console</div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed flex-1">View all reports, manage dispatchers, and export report data by date range.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 px-3 py-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white/80">
          Admin Login
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 md:mt-12 border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl shadow-[0_18px_42px_rgba(15,23,42,0.09)] max-w-4xl mx-auto p-5 md:p-6">
      <div class="text-[0.8rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-600 mb-4">Need to move fast?</div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 bg-slate-50 text-slate-600">
          <strong class="block text-slate-800 mb-1">1.</strong>
          Pick the role that matches your task and jump straight into the live interface.
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 bg-slate-50 text-slate-600">
          <strong class="block text-slate-800 mb-1">2.</strong>
          Keep supporting details ready—location, description, and attachments—to speed up validation.
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 bg-slate-50 text-slate-600">
          <strong class="block text-slate-800 mb-1">3.</strong>
          Use the quick jump chips to hop between report, dispatcher, and admin flows in a click.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-[0.7rem] font-bold tracking-[0.14em] text-slate-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white/80">v1.0 · Real-time via Pusher · SVS (Smart Verification System)</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
